{"text_id":248378,"tokens":["In"," this"," work",","," we"," investigate"," the"," problem"," of"," extending"," convolution"," operations"," to"," compact"," groups"," and"," their"," co","set"," spaces",","," and"," its"," implications"," for"," the"," Fourier"," algebra","."," The"," Fourier"," algebra",","," a"," fundamental"," tool"," in"," the"," study"," of"," compact"," groups",","," is"," an"," essential"," algebra"," that"," captures"," the"," harmonic"," analysis"," of"," the"," group","."," However",","," its"," extension"," to"," co","set"," spaces"," is"," not"," straightforward"," and"," presents"," several"," challenges",".","\n\n","Our"," approach"," is"," centered"," on"," the"," concept"," of"," convolution"," of"," functions"," on"," compact"," groups","."," We"," propose"," a"," natural"," extension"," of"," this"," operation"," to"," co","set"," spaces",","," which"," allows"," us"," to"," define"," a"," convolution"," algebra"," on"," these"," spaces","."," This"," extension"," is"," based"," on"," the"," properties"," of"," the"," group"," action"," and"," the"," existence"," of"," a"," Haar"," measure"," on"," the"," co","set"," space",".","\n\n","We"," then"," proceed"," to"," show"," that"," this"," convolution"," algebra"," is"," isomorphic"," to"," a"," sub","algebra"," of"," the"," Fourier"," algebra"," of"," the"," group","."," This"," result"," provides"," a"," powerful"," tool"," for"," studying"," the"," Fourier"," algebra"," of"," co","set"," spaces","."," Furthermore",","," we"," establish"," a"," Plan","cher","el"," theorem"," for"," this"," convolution"," algebra",","," which"," allows"," us"," to"," characterize"," the"," dual"," object"," of"," the"," co","set"," space",".","\n\n","Our"," motivation"," for"," this"," research"," is"," twofold","."," Firstly",","," the"," extension"," of"," convolution"," operations"," to"," co","set"," spaces"," has"," important"," implications"," for"," the"," study"," of"," harmonic"," analysis"," and"," the"," representation"," theory"," of"," compact"," groups","."," Secondly",","," the"," development"," of"," a"," convolution"," algebra"," on"," co","set"," spaces"," provides"," a"," new"," framework"," for"," studying"," the"," Fourier"," algebra",","," which"," is"," a"," fundamental"," object"," in"," the"," study"," of"," compact"," groups",".","\n\n","In"," summary",","," this"," work"," proposes"," a"," natural"," extension"," of"," convolution"," operations"," to"," co","set"," spaces",","," establishes"," a"," convolution"," algebra"," on"," these"," spaces",","," and"," demonstrates"," its"," isomorphism"," to"," a"," sub","algebra"," of"," the"," Fourier"," algebra","."," These"," results"," provide"," a"," powerful"," tool"," for"," studying"," the"," Fourier"," algebra"," of"," co","set"," spaces",","," with"," important"," implications"," for"," the"," study"," of"," harmonic"," analysis"," and"," the"," representation"," theory"," of"," compact"," groups","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}